high_descs: walk to the room with a wooden diningtable
pick up the knife from the wooden table
walk with knife to a box that has apple in it
Close the box and walk with the apple.
walk with the knife to the sink in the bathroom
Put the knife standing up on the bathroom sink.
walk out the bathroom and open the box with apple.
take an apple out of the box
Take the piece of fruit to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the apple in, then close the microwave.
Open the microwave and take the piece of fruit out of the sink. Walk with the fruit.
Walk with the apple to the bathroom and put the apple next to the knife on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Get apple next to knife in the sink.

high_descs: Go across to the diningtable in front of the fridge.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Go toward the hall, turn left at the dresser to the apple in the floor.
Slice the apple in the cardboard box.
Turn right at the cardboard box to the sink in the bathroom.
Place the knife on the left side of the sink.
Go back to the apple in the cardboard box.
Pick up a slice of the apple.
Head back to the fridge and go across to the rectangle table with the microwave.
Place the apple in the microwave, heat the apple, and pick the apple back up.
Head back to the sink and turn right.
Place the apple on the sink between the left faucet handle and the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of apple on the sink in the bathroom.

high_descs: Head straight down the hall until the end, turning left to the circular diningtable just ahead.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Return to the hall and go straight all the way until taking a left into the short path ahead.
Slice the green apple in the box.
Turn right to enter the sink.
Place the knife down on the sink.
Return the apple to the box.
Pick up one slice of the green apple.
Return to the room where you got the knife, continuing past the table to the microwave in the corner.
Use the microwave on the apple slice and remove the apple.
Return to the bathroom you placed the knife in the sink.
Place the apple on the sink next to the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved Apple slice on a Sink.
